  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-8 clean, bounded applicability)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This clean negative-control package declares an explicit operating envelope (flow rate 2–8 L/min, rotational speed 2000–3500 RPM, hematocrit 35–45%) with concrete applicability constraints, and all validation activities cover boundary and interior points of that envelope. All 13 credibility factors are assessed with achievedLevel >= requiredLevel. Decision: Accepted.",
