      "name": "VAD CFD operating envelope — bounded flow, speed, and hematocrit",
      "description": "Concrete bounded operating envelope within which CFD hemolysis predictions are credible. Validation experiments and simulations cover all five nominal operating points and both boundary corners of the envelope.",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "parameterName": "Flow rate",
          "lowerBound": 2.0,
          "upperBound": 8.0,
