            40,
            45
          ]
        }
      ],
      "coverageStatement": "Validation dataset includes bench experiments at all nine boundary-corner and mid-point combinations of the flow-rate and rotational-speed axes, at both hematocrit boundary values (35% and 45%) and the nominal value (40%). Full envelope coverage confirmed."
    }
