      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/sqa-level2",
      "rationale": "CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is managed under version-controlled repository with tagged release. Unit test suite covers 94% of solver modules. Change control log maintained. Achieved Gradation 3: full regression test suite with automated CI pipeline, exceeding the Gradation 2 requirement for MRL 3 at High decision consequence."
