      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/code-verification-level2",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) confirms correct implementation of rotating-frame Navier-Stokes equations. Observed convergence order 1.97–1.98 matches theoretical second-order scheme. Benchmark comparison against FDA round-robin CFD challenge (Stewart et al. 2012) also performed. Achieved Gradation 3, exceeding required Gradation 2."
