      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/input-equivalency-level3",
      "rationale": "Formal parameter equivalency matrix prepared comparing validation experiment conditions to COU operating conditions. Flow rate, rotational speed, hematocrit, temperature, and pump geometry all confirmed equivalent or bounding relative to COU. Operating envelope boundary points tested in validation experiments explicitly bracket the five COU operating points. No extrapolation beyond validated envelope required for COU predictions. Equivalency documented in the validation plan (VP-VAD-CFD-2023). Achieved Gradation 3 meets required Gradation 3."
